section.section:
A claimant who has also filed a claim with a new home warranty security plan shall include with the claim against the Guaranty Fund:
a copy or description of the claim filed with the new home warranty security plan;
any documents submitted by the claimant in support of the warranty claim, including engineering or inspection reports;
any documents submitted on behalf of the home builder or warranty plan in connection with the warranty claim, including engineering or inspection reports;
disclosure of any recoveries received in connection with the warranty claim; and
if all or part of the warranty claim was denied, a copy of the denial.
